OL,4,CQuarantine hotel rules face legal
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,6, A law firm representing travellers is
OL,7, challenging the UK's quarantine hotel
OL,8, policy and seeking a judicial review.
OL,10,FCurrently, passengers must spend 11
OL,11,Fnights in quarantine hotels on
OL,12,Freturning from red list countries,
OL,13,Fdespite being fully vaccinated and
OL,14,Ftesting negative for Covid.
OL,16,FLondon-based firm PGMBM says this is an
OL,17,F"unlawful deprivation of liberty".
OL,19,FOn Thursday, the cost of staying in a
OL,20,Fquarantine hotel jumped from #1,750 to
OL,21,F#2,285.
